    "PerformanceTo demonstrate the capabilities of Cryptomite, we perform some benchmarking of our constructions on a Apple M2 Max with 64GB RAM processor.",
    "The throughput (output bits per second) of the extractors of Cryptomite are shown in Figure 4.",
    "It is calculated by averaging the run-time over 10 trials, for each input length, for input lengths up to 5 × 10 8.",
    "Note that when the input length is below 2 29 > 5 × 10 8 bits, the convolution-based extractors (Circulant, Dodis et al.",
    "and Toeplitz) perform operations over a finite field defined by the prime p = 3 × 2 30 + 1."
